txt.en: 'Hey, you there! Let me go! Calder Cob can vouch for me!'
'Just wait till the Blackwolds get here. Then I'll be free, and you'll be dead!'
'Think you can just lock me up, eh? You'll be sorry when me friends get here!'
'You soft fools will regret this. Us Blackwolds aren't as stupid as you think....'
